Skew/Kurtosis

There wasnt too much effect here honestly. In future studies it might be worth pushing around a bit more. But for the time being at least we know that these are at least mildly robust to skew/kurtosis.

Results here are for cells with 100 clusters of 30. I thought that was the most interesting. 100 of 100 was too large, 30 of 30 was too small (still looked ok though).
